{"tid":930984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【真‧揦口揦面】條脷舔到額頭 奇技男：我嚇到小朋友瀨尿","createTime":"2018-12-06T16:59:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T01:00:19.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ac9dd3ef72804cc0b6ac30cc2f43eef07c5c4d8c","tid":930984,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T16:59:18.000Z","msg":"舌頭舔鼻已算是難得奇技，尼泊爾一名男子甚至可舔到自己的額頭，絕對是神乎其技。他自稱舌頭是全球最長，希望憑這奇技可獲列入健力士世界紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n35歲卡圖沃（Yagya Bahadur Katuwal）自稱擁有全球最長舌頭，亦是唯一一個可舔自己額頭的人，「我覺得這樣非常好，我可以用嘴唇碰着鼻子，再舔額頭」。從影片看到他先伸出長長舌頭，再用力將面容「收縮」，讓舌頭可以舔到額頭位置。<br />\n<br />\n朋友拍下他的「絕技」上載分享，令卡圖沃成為紅人。不過身為校車司機的他被要求工作時不要大顯身手，因會嚇怕孩童，他就稱表演不單令小孩怕得「瀨尿」，有成人也曾被嚇得暈倒，「如果我在恐怖電影中演出，我不需要像其他演員一樣要化妝，也可嚇壞人」。<br />\n<br />\n到底卡圖沃是如何做到這奇技？朋友認為是他口內只有一顆牙齒，而卡圖沃就希望他的非凡技巧可獲健力士世界紀錄大全確認。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/539aG9k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F539aG9k.png&h=d64a842e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181207/58989678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181207%2F58989678&d=mH1e2yiDRGEDVvCN%2BholnwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=b1b9b7f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181207%2F58989678&h=3434b290\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181207/58989678</a>"},{"pid":"901201ae04ac57169978006acc0f35423041397a","tid":930984,"uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T17:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c2c89e43ceab66c19349441481080be51a7abde","tid":930984,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T17:02:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d268efb6dd5f6ca59e2fc2ae6a3c7579d237322","tid":930984,"uid":137731,"like":1,"dislik